serialport
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project:    serialport-rs — cross-platform serial port library
Source:     https://github.com/serialport/serialport-rs
License:    Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0)

`serialport 4.9.0` is a direct dependency of `host/Cargo.toml`, used for
USB-serial communication with the device (provisioning, PIN reset, history
export). It is used as an unmodified upstream library dependency, not
vendored or modified in this repository. See
`docs/licensing/DEPENDENCY-AUDIT.md` for the GPLv3-compatibility reasoning
(MPL-2.0 is file-level copyleft and GPL-combination-safe by default). The
full MPL-2.0 license text is available at
<https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/>.

