Bundled/embedded font assets
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
`firmware/gen_emoji_font.c` (invoked from `firmware/build.rs`) rasterizes a
combined bitmap font, baked into the firmware binary, from two source fonts:

Noto Emoji
  File:       firmware/assets/NotoEmoji-Regular.ttf (bundled in this repo)
  Copyright:  Copyright 2013 Google Inc. All Rights Reserved.
  License:    SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1 (OFL 1.1) — full text
              accompanies the font at
              firmware/assets/NotoEmoji-LICENSE.txt, per the OFL's own
              redistribution condition (license + copyright notice must
              travel with the font).

DejaVu Sans
  File:       NOT bundled in this repo (confirmed via `git ls-tree -r
              HEAD`) — read from a system-installed path
              (`/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSans.ttf`, package
              `fonts-dejavu-core` on Debian/Ubuntu) at firmware build time
              only. A curated subset of its ASCII glyphs is rasterized into
              the same combined bitmap font described above.
  Copyright:  Copyright (c) 2003 by Bitstream, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
              DejaVu's own changes are public domain.
  License:    Bitstream Vera Fonts Copyright license. Text + full context
              (why it's noted here despite not being an in-tree asset) at
              docs/licensing/DejaVuSans-LICENSE.txt.
